You're Not Really a Man-Eater, Are You?

\N<Luna>Sigh, I'm a bit tired... Hey, Shouta-kun, shall we take a
little break?
\N<Luna>Geez, don't say weird things... Of course not~
Shall we take a short break in front of the pond?

\N<Shouta>Tch, it's not something erotic? ...Well then, instead, I'll
show you something♪
\N<Luna>..."Show"? What on earth are you going to show...?

\N<Shouta>The results of my training! Watch closely, okay? With my
skills, I can catch the fish in this pond in no time...♪

Shouta, suddenly looking proud, stripped off his clothes and
jumped into the pond.

\N<Luna>He's stripping down without a care... At his age, I guess he
doesn't mind~ (His "little buddy" is still small too... He
acts grown-up, but he's still just a... kid)
\N<Shouta>Ah, damn it... Hey! Don't run away! Wait!
\N<Luna>Hehe... For all his talk, he's still got a long way to go~
A reminiscence scene has been added.
After that, the two of them took a short break.
"1_t=10_subject=The way you struggle between ideals and reality might be cute"
"1_t=5_subject=I want to support him and quickly return to our original happy life"
"1_t=6_subject=There's no one else who makes me feel safe just by being together"
1 new notification: There is a new post on SNS.

\N<Luna>Actually, let's skip the break~ Let's finish today's quest
quickly and rest up at home~

\N<Shouta>Eh- That's so cruel~~ It was just a little joke~ We're
almost at the mid-boss, that's just not right...

\N<Luna>It's your fault for saying weird things, Shouta-kun~~ Come
on, let's keep going a bit longer~
